Package: kapow
Title: kapow detonates objects into variables and assigns them to a particular environment.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("David", "Ranzolin", email = "daranzolin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: It is sometimes a tad cumbersome to extract and assign particular variables from a data frame or list. Towards that end, kapow seamlessly explodes your environments with new variables.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports: dplyr,
    rlang,
    beepr
